endpoints.docs: Unstable Upserts a new scenario for a sandbox, keying off of the optionally provided scenario id. If an id is provided and has a match, the scenario will be updated. If no id is provided or no match is found, a new scenario will be appended to the end. Note that a full replacement of the scenario is performed, so any fields not provided will be removed or overwritten with default values.
